// jit_ppc.cpp — ARM->PPC JIT for Wii/Broadway  
// Fixed revision 4.2:
// 1. Fixed Thumb BLX suffix mask from 0x1C (B offset) to 0x1D (BLX suffix).
// 2. Fixed Thumb BLX Rm (Hi-register op) to correctly set LR = (curPC + 2) | 1.
// 3. Fixed JitHelp_commit CPSR mode sync to call interp->setCpsr() and prevent banked register stack corruption (Vector 0x18 crash).
// 4. Fixed NDS Dual-Core cycle accounting & interleaving in runJitNds() so IPC SYNC timeouts on ARM7 are eliminated.
// 5. Fixed Spin Loop False Escapes in runCpu() to avoid thrashing 2-instruction spin loops.

